---
title: One-Pot Chorizo & Tomato Penne with Hidden Veggies & Parmesan Cheese
description: Cheesy, rich and red, it’s a tomato sauce that’s very easy on the tastebuds. There’s tomato and leek stirred through alongside
mild chorizo, toss everything in a bowl of penne pasta and dinner just became irresistible.
